CRUD
----
Create -- post
Read -- get
Update -- put/patch
Delete -- delete

put -- update/replace
patch-- update/modify

In Put -- all the properties of object to be provided while making request
record exist -- will update/replace
record does not exist -- will create

{
    "Name": "Mahesh",
    "Job": "Automation",
    "Location": "Chennai",
    "Phone": 9000
}

In patch- specify only the properties that you want to update.
{
    "Addess": "Pune"
}